profile:
My Home Solution is owned and operated by Tomas Barrueco. Tomas has been in the renovation business for more than 20 years and during that time has developed a deep set of skills and the ability to handle almost all aspects of most renovations.

What sets My Home Solution apart is their ability to listen closely to what the customer wants, provide advice based on experience and bring to the job practical and functional design sense and attention to detail. The combination of which provides the best outcome for the customer.

We are known for:

Quality workmanship
Use of quality hardware
Attention to detail
Being on time
Personable nature
Going above and beyond for our customers
services:
Carpentry
Kitchen & Bathroom 
Tiling & Flooring
Doors & Windows 
Drywall & Painting
payment_method: Cheque, Cash, E-Transfer, Credit Card (Master Card, Visa)
